		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用左右两臂进行至多2段挥舞攻击，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用右臂的长棍进行下劈，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用长棍进行旋、挑、旋至多三段的攻击，攻击依次造成<span color="#ff9999">60%,70%,<br/>90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用长棍进行穿戳攻击，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，冲刺结束后可能进行一次挥扫，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用盾锯进行3段的旋扫攻击，其依次造成<span color="#ffacff">50%,50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用盾锯进行上挑、下落至多2段的攻击，其依次造成<span color="#ffacff">70%,90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">攻坚机关使用盾锯进行重重下落，造成<span color="#ffacff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
