		<RichText x="66" y="912" width="409" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">荒芒性质：<span color="#ffbfbf">2次</span><span>芒荒攻击可以瘫痪相反属性的攻坚机关，约25s-30s后恢复荒芒属性。</span></p>
